snippet.title: Novice Mistakes to Avoid as Software Developer
snippet.description:
Today's short video talks about mistakes that novices can make when starting out as iOS Developers learning Swift.

Here's the list of things to watch out for:
1. Setting correct expectations
2. Don't bite off more than you can chew
3. Take time to understand solutions from Google
